    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "76837d09-752e-4d92-bcef-543d907f1aee",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Good Soup",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK",
        "PublicId": "108645088589",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Bangkok/_scene_tiger.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8f5d0794-b2d5-4b1e-8878-acefc1b88a1b).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47.\rYour targets are Akkarat Chaikarn, Charoen Kongkatitum, and Madee Phyachai. This trio have been running a secret soup trafficking business right under the nose of the Himmapan Hotel. They sneak the head chef&apos;s award winning soup out through the underground maintenance rooms and sell it to street vendors at a hefty upcharge. The head chef has recieved intel that his patented soup is out on the streets, besmirching his fine name. He can not let this happen. Take them out.\rGood luck, 47.",
